GITTERY
-------

- To make local branch goo

    $ git branch foo
    $ git checkout foo
    $ ...
    $ git commit -a -m "did work in foo"

- To send branch to the mothership

    $ git push origin foo

- To work with branch elsewhere

    $ git pull
    $ git checkout foo

